title: A2141 820-01700-a 20v 300ma
message:
There doesnt seems to be any kind of corrosion or spillage on the board. I dont have a known good battery for this but I have by-3200 here connected to bench supply.
current at 300ma without battery and goes up to 1.2a then back to 30ma with battery in, same with original charger. U9500 @70c heat. is this a common issue on this board ?
L9530  PP1V8_SSD0  is reading short, remove and pad 2 reading short to ground. Dead nand?

title: A2141 820-01700-a 20v 300ma
message: If is pure short, something must heat injecting voltage.
